Backup saving and management
This type of service allows the Owner to save and manage backups of EasyVFR 4 website and application on external servers managed by the service provider itself. The backups may include the source code and content as well as the data that the User provides to EasyVFR 4 website and application.
EasyVFR cloud
Automatically :
EasyVFR stores routes, filed flightplans and aircraft profiles to servers located in the Netherlands owned by PocketFMS whenever there is an internet connection available and the associated item is saved.
Manually:
Logbook (includes tracking details), user waypoints, breadcrumb details are only stored on EasyVFR cloud when explicitly executed by the user.
This processing constitutes:
a Sharing in California
